ht"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>Business Info</h2><p>Leonard Lake Reserve<br />8001 Reeves Canyon Road<br />Redwood Valley, CA 95470<br />(707) 513-6500<br /><a href="mailto:info@leonardlakereserve.com">info@leonardlakereserve.com</a></p></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_2_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-phone et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>About Us</h2><p>Leonard Lake Reserve is a unique vacation rental, group lodging, and wedding venue in Mendocino County. Beautifully surrounded by old growth redwood forests and an expansive 18 acre lake.</p></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_3_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_2_tb_footer  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-phone et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>Site Links</h2><ul style="list-style: none;"><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQ</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/about-us/">About</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/contact-us/">Contact</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/calendar/">Calendar</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/volunteer/">Volunteer</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://leonardlakereserve.com/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></li><li style="margin-left: -15px;"><a href="https://www.bonfire.com/store/leonard-lake-reserve/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Merchandise</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_4_tb_footer  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div 